partner in that con game?
-Oh, no, not yet.

34:07.128 --> 34:10.923
Black girl's given us
a number of addresses
and hangouts on him.

34:10.923 --> 34:12.091
She really
wants to help herself.

34:12.091 --> 34:14.886
-You did good work
on this, Diane.
-It was James's plan.

34:16.220 --> 34:18.765
Captain? We need to talk?

34:18.765 --> 34:20.683
Yeah.

34:23.061 --> 34:25.354
On this cop's transfer,

34:25.354 --> 34:30.401
I need to tell you,
I don't think
it was your finest hour.

34:30.401 --> 34:32.779
Why is that?

34:32.779 --> 34:35.740
The both of us know the job
has an Ethical Awareness
Course...

34:35.740 --> 34:37.575
for this kind of cop
and this kind of situation.

34:37.575 --> 34:40.161
The sensitivity class isn't
going to do it for this guy.

34:40.161 --> 34:43.581
Arthur, if Szymanski's
like you say he is,

34:43.581 --> 34:46.542
don't like black people
much to begin with,

34:46.542 --> 34:50.546
plus resentful now,
from his point of view,
a black boss loused his life up.

34:50.546 --> 34:54.801
Is that the kind of cop you want
walking around a neighborhood
don't need any extra problems?

34:54.801 --> 34:58.096
So, you're concerned I'd be
lowering the quality of life
in Bed-Stuy?

34:58.096 --> 35:02.433
I'm just pointing out
what I know you know already.

35:02.433 --> 35:06.145
As bosses, our decisions
have consequences outside
the rooms we make 'em in.

35:06.145 --> 35:08.856
If you wanna discuss
the quality of policing
of black neighborhoods,

35:08.856 --> 35:11.400
we can take that up in length,
but what's going on here...

35:11.400 --> 35:15.029
is what always goes on
with the black man on this job
who asks for an accommodation.

35:15.029 --> 35:17.406
It's assumed he's got
a hidden agenda.

35:17.406 --> 35:20.660
Look, I came here asking
for you to look at using
your juice to hurt this guy...

35:20.660 --> 35:25.581
and remind you that people
neither you nor I know
are liable to pay the tab.

35:25.581 --> 35:29.585
Pretending it's about you being
black so you don't have to face
what it is you're doing,

35:29.585 --> 35:31.087
that's on you.

35:35.049 --> 35:38.678
Okay, okay.

35:38.678 --> 35:41.430
-Transfer him
to this precinct.
-Transfer him here?

35:41.430 --> 35:46.102
Yeah, that way I can deal
every day with the consequences
of the decisions we made here.

35:49.689 --> 35:52.024
I think over time,

35:52.024 --> 35:56.654
knowing the kind of man you are
at heart, might turn out good
for Szymanski.

35:56.654 --> 36:02.243
-Might be good for you too.
-I think we've looked enough
into my heart and soul.

36:02.243 --> 36:03.870
Is sending him here
acceptable to you?

36:03.870 --> 36:07.206
Yeah.
I can make that happen.

36:25.433 --> 36:27.476
-Hey, Greg.
-Hey, Abby.

36:27.476 --> 36:29.854
-You have a good shift?
-Yeah, yeah.

36:29.854 --> 36:34.025
We shut down one of those
"found money" con teams.

36:34.025 --> 36:36.861
-You just on your way in?
-4:00 to 12:00.

36:36.861 --> 36:38.946
Yeah. You like it there
in Anticrime?

36:38.946 --> 36:41.657
Yeah, I do.

36:41.657 --> 36:44.952
Greg, could you find time
for dinner sometime
in the next while?

36:44.952 --> 36:48.080
Sure, of course.

36:48.080 --> 36:52.585
Uh, what's the occasion,
just a pleasant meal
between friends?

36:52.585 --> 36:55.254
Well, I hoped that it
was a pleasant meal...

36:55.254 --> 36:57.798
that might result
in a special occasion.

36:57.798 --> 37:03.512
Well, that's very mysterious
and interesting.

37:03.512 --> 37:07.016
Well, I-I'm not comfortable
being more specific.

37:07.016 --> 37:10.436
Well, sure.
Um, just let me know
the day.

37:10.436 --> 37:14.649
I got broad areas
of empty calendar.
Thanks a lot.

37:14.649 --> 37:16.609
Sure.
Have a good shift, Abby.
Night, Greg.

37:16.609 --> 37:18.236
Have a good night.

37:30.748 --> 37:32.875
What's going on, Andy?

37:36.295 --> 37:38.881
(clears throat)

37:38.881 --> 37:43.719
Uh, you think it's possible...

37:43.719 --> 37:49.350
people that have passed on,
making contact with the living?

37:49.350 --> 37:52.436
-You mean like ghosts?
-Yeah, more so by way
of your dreams.

37:53.479 --> 37:56.732
-I don't know.
-[ Sighs ]

37:56.732 --> 38:01.737
Me working these robberies,
Andy Jr. being killed
in a bar,

38:01.737 --> 38:05.992
I can see rationally how
a dream might manifest
from that.

38:05.992 --> 38:08.327
What happens
in the dream?

38:08.327 --> 38:12.999
We're in contact.
Don't exactly get along.

38:14.417 --> 38:16.919
Ah, I don't believe
it's possible.

38:16.919 --> 38:21.007
I used to dream
about my wife quite a bit.
Yeah?

38:21.007 --> 38:25.177
Never seemed to have
any particular meaning.

38:25.177 --> 38:27.847
Me cooking meals for her,
taking her out on walks
and stuff.

38:27.847 --> 38:32.768
So, she never came
with tips on horses to bet?
Nothing like that?

38:32.768 --> 38:34.812
Nah.

39:01.297 --> 39:03.424
Something alcoholic?

39:03.424 --> 39:06.510
-We collared those guys
stuck you up.
-Is that right?

39:06.510 --> 39:09.096
Collared 'em on a bus.

39:09.096 --> 39:10.681
Large vehicle.

39:16.062 --> 39:18.647
Son!
(chuckles)

39:18.647 --> 39:20.941
I am so relieved.

39:22.818 --> 39:25.363
You know
who's in the bathroom
that I brought with me?

39:25.363 --> 39:28.657
-Who?
-Sylvia and the baby.

39:28.657 --> 39:32.370
They're both
in the ladies' room. I told her
to keep his eyes covered.

39:32.370 --> 39:35.998
To be truthful,
I-I don't think
they should be present here.

39:39.251 --> 39:41.754
Think I brought 'em
to expose Theo to liquor?

39:41.754 --> 39:43.881
Look, I--I don't wanna
fight with you.

39:43.881 --> 39:48.177
Well, I can't do nothing right.
I brought him to meet
his brother.

39:48.177 --> 39:50.805
Think seeing me murdered
is gonna make a happy memory?

39:54.433 --> 39:58.687
(gasping)

39:58.687 --> 40:01.107
This is where
you were murdered.

40:01.107 --> 40:03.192
I just don't wanna
complicate it.

40:10.449 --> 40:13.661
These murdering bastards.

40:13.661 --> 40:16.831
What the system
lets walk around.

40:16.831 --> 40:18.958
Dad, I don't wanna
complicate it.

40:18.958 --> 40:21.085
I'm a police officer,
you understand that?

40:21.919 --> 40:25.506
-It makes certain claims
on my time.
-Oh, here we go.

40:25.506 --> 40:29.635
-These are the skells
killed you.
-Gee, Pop, really?

40:29.635 --> 40:31.929
You think they'll stop
with killing you? This is
why I have to do this.

40:31.929 --> 40:34.515
That's crap.

40:40.604 --> 40:43.232
The balls you sit here.

40:55.161 --> 40:57.163
-Great, Dad.
-You shut up.

40:57.163 --> 40:59.748
You don't know nothing
how the world is.

40:59.748 --> 41:03.252
Yeah, I was really
sheltered being murdered.

41:07.756 --> 41:11.510
Oh, my God.
What did I do?

41:11.510 --> 41:13.637
What did I do?

41:20.769 --> 41:24.565
-What's your problem?
-I gave you my seat
at the diner.

41:24.565 --> 41:26.984
We're gonna be
lifetime companions?

41:26.984 --> 41:32.072
That's Jesus Christ, Dad.
Congratulations pissin' off
Jesus Christ.

41:35.534 --> 41:39.038
That's your boss?
He's traveling with you?

41:42.666 --> 41:44.710
Dead as when he started.

41:45.544 --> 41:48.589
-What did I do?
-What did I tell ya?

41:48.589 --> 41:50.758
I don't recall.

41:53.802 --> 41:57.223
Talk through me.
Talk through me.

41:57.223 --> 41:59.558
Please give me another chance.

42:01.393 --> 42:03.646
What did you just have?

42:21.997 --> 42:27.294
I-I loved him,
as bad as I am.

42:27.294 --> 42:29.797
Oh, my poor boy.

42:54.863 --> 42:56.865
(sniffles)

42:56.865 --> 42:58.826
Good boy.

43:01.412 --> 43:03.956
Good boy.

43:04.873 --> 43:07.293
(sniffles)

43:07.293 --> 43:09.461
Good boy.

43:19.054 --> 43:22.057
♪♪
